<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.10.7">
<l>iruṅkaimmā karimuṉintu pariyaik kīṟi yiṉaviṭaika ḷēḻaṭarttu marutañ cāyttu</l>
<l>varuñcakaṭa miṟavutaittu mallai yaṭṭu vañcañcey kañcaṉukku nañcā ṉāṉai</l>
<l>karuṅkamuku pacumpāḷai veṇmut tīṉṟu kāyellām marakatamāyp pavaḷaṅ kāṭṭa</l>
<l>ceruntimika moṭṭalarttun tēṉkoḷ cōlait tirukkōva lūrataṉuḷ kaṇṭēṉ nāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who, having raged at the huge black-trunked elephant,</l>
<l rend="indent">split the horse, destroyed a group of seven bulls,</l>
<l rend="indent">pushed over the marutu trees,</l>
<l>Having kicked the advancing cart to break [it], [and] destroyed the wrestlers,</l>
<l rend="indent">was poison to Kaṁsa who committed treachery,</l>
<l>I saw in Tirukkōvalūr with honeyed groves</l>
<l rend="indent">where the champaka’s many buds bloom,</l>
<l>Where dark areca [tree’s] green bracts and fruit, producing white seeds,</l>
<l rend="indent">all appear [like] emeralds and corals.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
